{"ID":270190, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"190\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs189.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs191.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 190<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">They who have tabernacles, have power over those who have not. The doctrine of eternal\n  judgment;<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> Acts 2:41.<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span> Peter preached, Repent, and be baptized in the name of Jesus Christ, for the\n  remission of sins,<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span> &amp;c.; but in Acts 3:19 he says, Repent, and be converted, that your sins may be\n  blotted out when the times of redemption shall come, and he shall send Jesus,<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> &amp;c.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">The Three Personages<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">Everlasting covenant<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> was made between three personages before the organization of this earth,\n  and relates to their dispensation of things to men on the earth; these personages, according to\n  Abraham&rsquo;s record, are called God the first, the Creator;<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> God the second, the Redeemer;<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span> and God\n  the third, the witness or Testator.<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span>&mdash;MSS<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">The Twelve Next to the First Presidency<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">President Joseph Smith now arriving, proceeded to state to the conference at considerable\n  length, the object of their present meeting, and, in addition to what President Young had stated in\n  the morning, said that the time had come when the Twelve should be called upon to stand in their\n  place next to the First Presidency, and attend to the settling of immigrants and the business of the\n  Church at the stakes, and assist to bear off the kingdom victoriously to the nations, and as they had\n  been faithful, and had borne the burden in the heat of the day,<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> that it was right that they should have\n  an opportunity of providing something for themselves and families,<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span> and at the same time relieve\n  him, so that he might attend to the business of translating.<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Moved, seconded and carried, that the conference approve of the instructions of President Smith\n  in relation to the Twelve, and that they proceed accordingly to attend to the duties of their office.\n  (Aug. 16, 1841.) DHC 4:403.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Trust in God When Sick<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">Sunday, Sept. 5, 1841. I preached to a large congregation at the stand, on the science and\n  practice of medicine, desiring to persuade the Saints to trust in God<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> when sick, and not in an arm\n  of flesh,<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> and live by faith<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span> and not by medicine, or poison; and when they were sick, and had\n  called for the Elders to pray<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span> for them, and they were not healed, to use herbs and mild\n  food.<span class=\"footRef\">16<\/span>&mdash;DHC 4:414.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110182\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110182)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110182)\">Heb. 6:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108964\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108964)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108964)\">Acts 2:41<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108951\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108951)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108951)\">Acts 2:38<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108972\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108972)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108972)\">Acts 3:19<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106006\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106006)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106006)\">Gen. 9:16<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110339\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110339)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110339)\">Heb. 13:20<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113414\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113414)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113414)\">D&amp;C 22:1<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114263\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114263)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114263)\">D&amp;C 66:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107174\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107174)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107174)\">Isa. 40:28<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111363\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111363)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111363)\">Jacob 2:5<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106781\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106781)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106781)\">Ps. 78:35<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107204\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107204)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107204)\">Isa. 48:17<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111024\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111024)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111024)\">1 Ne. 17:30<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113206\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113206)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113206)\">D&amp;C 10:70<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114274\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114274)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114274)\">D&amp;C 66:13<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108845\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108845)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108845)\">John 15:26<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108853\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108853)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108853)\">John 16:13-14<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110628\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110628)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110628)\">1 Jn. 5:8-9<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116849\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116849)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116849)\">Moses 6:61<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108129\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108129)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108129)\">Matt. 20:12<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114368\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114368)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114368)\">D&amp;C 75:28<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113804\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113804)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113804)\">D&amp;C 43:13<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114354\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114354)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114354)\">D&amp;C 73:4<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114979\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114979)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114979)\">D&amp;C 90:13<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111589\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111589)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111589)\">Mosiah 7:19<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112183\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112183)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112183)\">Alma 36:3<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111142\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111142)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111142)\">2 Ne. 4:34<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113065\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113065)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113065)\">D&amp;C 1:19<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109229\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109229)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109229)\">Rom. 1:17<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110380\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110380)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110380)\">James 5:14<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113756\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113756)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:v